title: Paleo - Misery, Missouri  aac
description:
Created by master songwriter David Strackany (Paleo). 

Released in October 2004. Only 1000 copies printed with no plans of re-release. 

See also his Song Diary project, which involved touring the nation and sleeping in his car for an entire year all while writing and recording a new song each day. 

All songs are available for free on his website: http://www.paleo.ws/
